satisfiesAll

public SubstitutionList satisfiesAll(Decomposition decomposition,
                                     Substitution alpha,
                                     AxiomSet axioms,
                                     boolean negation)
Tests if some conditions can be infered from this State and AxiomSet modulo a Substitution alpha.

Parameters:
decomposition - the Decomposition to be tested.
alpha - the previously computed Substitution.
axioms - the AxiomSet.
negation - true to indicate that the Problem use negation facts.
Returns:
If some conditions can be infered, it returns all of the matching Substitutions else it returns an empty Substitutionlist.

satisfies

public SubstitutionList satisfies(Literal literal,
                                  Substitution alpha,
                                  boolean negation)
It searches all Atom s in this matching a Literal modulo the Substitution alpha.

Parameters:
literal - the matching Atom.
alpha - the Substitution.
negation - true to unify using discriminent negation.
Returns:
If such an Atom is found, the matching Substitution s are returned, otherwise, it returns an empty SubstitutionList.
